{"tid":2316533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周梓樂死因研訊：代表警方的律師指打算一併代表消防 後覺不妥 致研訊需押後","createTime":"2020-12-08T03:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T03:58:32.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a948de1b6ea213d7f02f5af49a78d87dc3904b","tid":2316533,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:09:21.000Z","msg":"周梓樂死因研訊因消防未能派法律代表到庭押後至下周<br />\n<br />\n科大男生周梓樂死因研訊繼續，死因庭上周將消防列為有利害關係一方，但消防早上未能派法律代表到庭。<span class=\"gold\">代表警方的律師指，原先打算一併代表消防</span>，但其後發現安排並不妥當，消防需要委派獨立法律代表。消防處代表則稱，律政司轉告需要多一星期準備，了解案情及相關資料。死因裁判官高偉雄質疑，律政司應知道死因研訊的急切性，法庭不能給予太多時間，批評消防的陳詞不負責任，決定將研訊押至下周一，又指研訊應不能如期在下周五完成。<br />\n<br />\n高偉雄表示，研訊期間在尚德停車場發現多4枝固定的閉路電視鏡頭，分別位於地下及二樓後樓梯門口，原本打算今天播放，為尊重消防處需要有獨立法律代表，同時表明，曾作供的救護員需要再上庭。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2369738\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2369738&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7ByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=fec49651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2369738</a>"},{"pid":"97fbf18127254647fde947ed45351c36fbd48b64","tid":2316533,"uid":55597,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:10:29.000Z","msg":"你有咩資格代表消防？"},{"pid":"a6106183b0c39786c923d84a88dac282152b3633","tid":2316533,"uid":55597,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:11:03.000Z","msg":"岩岩有單消防車撞死人，呢單你去代表消防就岩啦"},{"pid":"453fc83af139bf56177a73ba391c752e6f12a766","tid":2316533,"uid":141837,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:12:55.000Z","msg":"周星馳功夫足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be856b4a3bd44bfb8ece3eda4681baee21d7431d","tid":2316533,"uid":255402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d37ef512e9ba128e033e28816380454a46596c","tid":2316533,"uid":59633,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"個律師食錯咩藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08e0d94b9494cd6239f8490d881236033c98cb4","tid":2316533,"uid":108606,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:42:52.000Z","msg":"所有（無）紀律部隊都係狗隊的手下，要聽狗隊支笛，代表埋有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd8af672f71e126add34ce13845b41eb7de8732","tid":2316533,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:46:11.000Z","msg":"律政司平時就係咁嘥晒啲時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f49fb7ebd7616d21883abd64a0d6b00b7bb2201","tid":2316533,"uid":363335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:58:32.000Z","msg":"警隊想夾消防被代表，但係個官覺得唔妥"}]}